      "versionNonce": 1965378193,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1771934059126,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "LEGEND\n█ Blue (shared)    PollingBlockIngestor — polls Katana RPC, emits BlockInfo { Mined } into pipeline channel\n█ Green (sovereign) Sovereign mode: Atlantic SNOS proof → Celestia blob → in-memory / SQLite storage. No L2 settlement.\n█ Orange (persist)  Persistent mode: SNOS + Layout Bridge proof → Celestia/Noop → Piltover update_state() on L2/L1.\n█ Purple (TEE)      TEE mode: no external prover, no DA layer — TEE attestation proves block inside hardware enclave.\n█ Teal (DA)         CelestiaDA backend: CBOR-serialises packet, submits blob, returns DataAvailabilityPointer { height, commitment, ns }.\n█ Red (settlement)  PiltoverSettlement: queries Piltover contract, registers Integrity facts, calls update_state(), polls tx.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LEGEND\n█ Blue (shared)    PollingBlockIngestor — polls Katana RPC, emits BlockInfo { Mined } into pipeline channel\n█ Green (sovereign) Sovereign mode: Atlantic SNOS proof → Celestia blob → in-memory / SQLite storage. No L2 settlement.\n█ Orange (persist)  Persistent mode: SNOS + Layout Bridge proof → Celestia/Noop → Piltover update_state() on L2/L1.\n█ Purple (TEE)      TEE mode: no external prover, no DA layer — TEE attestation proves block inside hardware enclave.\n█ Teal (DA)         CelestiaDA backend: CBOR-serialises packet, submits blob, returns DataAvailabilityPointer { height, commitment, ns }.\n█ Red (settlement)  PiltoverSettlement: queries Piltover contract, registers Integrity facts, calls update_state(), polls tx.",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "baseline": 14,
      "index": "az",
      "autoResize": true
    },
